Radboud University）的科學家完成一項研究。他們檢視逾18萬人的基因資料，樣本來自英國生物樣本庫（UK Biobank）、基因技術公司「23andME」等。研究結果發現，吸食大麻與35種基因相關，其中以「CADM2」基因的連結最強。研究結果刊登於《自然-神經科學》（Nature Neuroscience）期刊。"},{"pid":"0d4786e83717a489ce996ade050c644a25a5fe60","tid":799662,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"手震係因為毒引起"},{"pid":"a407fe73d22133223501765d5a7e9f9eaed59f93","tid":799662,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d4786e83717a489ce996ade050c644a25a5fe60","tid":799662,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"手震係因為毒引起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"*癮"},{"pid":"6e87874d5a6af663ff977113e75d5356506e7faa","tid":799662,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d4786e83717a489ce996ade050c644a25a5fe60","tid":799662,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"手震係因為毒引起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩個阿伯唔係住係香港"},{"pid":"e9481491c0c47d017d4e0b71831e708a18268504","tid":799662,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"smoke weed everyday"},{"pid":"6f79571d4cf92ffac3c6e23de6442f8602dde2ea","tid":799662,"uid":65128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9456d4d226b596b332eae95d12f46d5d8db21421","tid":799662,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f7f38ff6f8997f4ed8eec3fdec22ba11be974a1","tid":799662,"uid":65128,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b296ff6d3f75f0c2178dc28dcf76e33a5454844","tid":799662,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,